{"tid":2465443,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"LG 水貨V50s 開CA & 5G 求教","createTime":"2021-03-28T10:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T18:59:20.000Z","uid":140722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8158267fe6101e178629b27cfa6cc7b8893509","tid":2465443,"uid":140722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"兩個月前入手左部V50s (LG U+版)<br />\n跟住上個月csl打黎摟續約， 開埋5G data plan<br />\n但插落部V50s之後仍然係收唔到5G, 本來有啲失望<br />\n<br />\n於是上網google睇下有冇辦法可以開到個5G出黎<br />\n<br />\n搵左好耐， 無意見到有台仔喺mobile01教改carrier policy.xml黎開2/3/4CA (佢地都係揸住V50s 水貨):<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=581&amp;t=6156226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mobile01.com%2Ftopicdetail.php%3Ff%3D581%26t%3D6156226&d=BSPHu9UqRwj8n7oVkU4q%2BRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=fc07c0f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=581&amp;t=6156226</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地加左好多7A4/8A2A/3A4/1A4唔同既CA組合入carrier policy<br />\n但我睇左好耐都唔係好明呢啲CA組合同band既關係係乜<br />\n<br />\n然後我將佢地upload上去既carrier policy隊左落我自己部機度， reboot之後居然收到空心5G signal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道CSL support 4G band 1/3/7/8, 5G有n1/n78, 但係要加啲乜野CA組合先可以喺香港用？ CA組合點睇？<br />\n佢地改既嗰個carrier policy又係邊part同5G有關？<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a417480f3a83ea04aa2e4ec810221b0f0034d2","tid":2465443,"uid":208940,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T11:03:28.000Z","msg":"好似LG已經退出手機業"},{"pid":"357ba88cde71f0d830b8629caa3253571b1130fe","tid":2465443,"uid":140722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7a417480f3a83ea04aa2e4ec810221b0f0034d2","tid":2465443,"uid":208940,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T11:03:28.000Z","msg":"好似LG已經退出手機業"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2021/01/21/lg-ces-mobilephone/mobile-phone/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F01%2F21%2Flg-ces-mobilephone%2Fmobile-phone%2Famp%2F&d=BSPHu9UqRwj8n7oVkU4q%2BRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=5ab1ee45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2021/01/21/lg-ces-mobilephone/mobile-phone/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n我問緊點改carrier policy, 唔係講佢退出手機業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4776af389f10a40eaa109d7a1d03ac7363f127bb","tid":2465443,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d8158267fe6101e178629b27cfa6cc7b8893509","tid":2465443,"uid":140722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"兩個月前入手左部V50s (LG U+版)<br />\n跟住上個月csl打黎摟續約， 開埋5G data plan<br />\n但插落部V50s之後仍然係收唔到5G, 本來有啲失望<br />\n<br />\n於是上網google睇下有冇辦法可以開到個5G出黎<br />\n<br />\n搵左好耐， 無意見到有台仔喺mobile01教改carrier policy.xml黎開2/3/4CA (佢地都係揸住V50s 水貨):<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=581&amp;t=6156226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mobile01.com%2Ftopicdetail.php%3Ff%3D581%26t%3D6156226&d=BSPHu9UqRwj8n7oVkU4q%2BRVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=fc07c0f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=581&amp;t=6156226</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地加左好多7A4/8A2A/3A4/1A4唔同既CA組合入carrier policy<br />\n但我睇左好耐都唔係好明呢啲CA組合同band既關係係乜<br />\n<br />\n然後我將佢地upload上去既carrier policy隊左落我自己部機度， reboot之後居然收到空心5G signal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道CSL support 4G band 1/3/7/8, 5G有n1/n78, 但係要加啲乜野CA組合先可以喺香港用？ CA組合點睇？<br />\n佢地改既嗰個carrier policy又係邊part同5G有關？<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"我想問下你已經解左bootloader,root左可以入system partition改野?"},{"pid":"ad69b20bef8449ce8b49c3e3992206fcdc722437","tid":2465443,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7a41748